headline: Sally Beauty and DoorDash Team Up to Deliver Fall Beauty Must-Haves on the Go
summary: Sally Beauty, the leading destination for professional-quality hair color, hair care, and nails, has partnered with DoorDash, a leading local commerce platform, to launch Beauty on the Go, a free pop-up event taking place in New York City from September 25–27.
